(firstQuint)Reserpine for the Treatment of Cocaine Dependence - 1.

 To assess the efficacy and safety of reserpine in reducing cocaine use in subjects with cocaine dependence.

 This is a double-blind, placebo-controlled, parallel-group design with a 2 week baseline period.

